OL,5,G1900 Scenic Ireland with Adrian Dunbar
OL,6,     FThe actor explores favourite
OL,7,     Fplaces in his homeland of Ireland,
OL,8,     Fsharing his passion for food,
OL,9,     Fhistory, and landscapes. His
OL,10,     Fjourney begins in the west at Wild
OL,11,     FAtlantic Way in Co Donegal.
OL,12,     F(Ep1/2)
OL,13,G2000 Cornwall: A Year by the Sea
OL,14,     FAt St Michael's Mount, a major
OL,15,     Fclear-up operation is needed
OL,16,     Ffollowing severe storms. And the
OL,17,     Fpicturesque harbour town of
OL,18,     FPadstow prepares for its annual
OL,19,     FMay Day Festival.
